{"tid":709093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"包容跨性別！英癌症基金會用「有子宮」代替「女性」","createTime":"2018-06-19T17:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T05:42:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"108256f7771b96d6b739540872b452bd3d899fac","tid":709093,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕性別平權的概念在世界上逐漸成為潮流，英國癌症研究基金會（Cancer Research UK）在宣導子宮頸檢查時，特意拿掉了「女性（Women）」這個詞彙，希望能對跨性別者更加包容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，英國癌症研究基金會新的子宮頸檢查宣導文案，不用「25至64歲的女性」的描述，而改用「每個25至64歲有子宮的人們」，增加了對於跨性別者與部分因故切除子宮的婦女的包容。<br />\n<br />\n英國癌症研究基金會的奧斯根（Fiona Osgun）表示，「子宮頸癌有可能在任何有子宮頸的人身上發生」，因此不只女性，他們也鼓勵性別認同為男性，但還是有子宮的人來檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2459669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2459669&d=f10hdI1SAMbs4T3xEmP7B2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=45b1463b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2459669&h=2e0b71ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2459669</a>"},{"pid":"073c38d9fde3b38f2dd9c07b4b10d76e56767658","tid":709093,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"跨性別=/=變性,可以係天生嗰啲雙性人,所以值得原諒"},{"pid":"b3ee7e8dee32110c96a3d9609e28cf7831d9f2d8","tid":709093,"uid":59030,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52617ad0407b0b63a70bbdcb6071f9395910789","tid":709093,"uid":163350,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"743486e0da1885c12df44fd86ad2c27c62a2a7ca","tid":709093,"uid":27915,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"男性=有賓周？"},{"pid":"0d704c923b7c57bd9131